overview.zh: eCell是Consensus Cell Network去中心化的区块链应用孵化器的基础治理通证，将用于项目孵化、对外投资、社区激励等。
overview.en: eCell is the foundation governance token for Consensus Cell Network's decentralized blockchain application Incubator, which will be used for project incubation, outbound investment, community motivation, and more.
